00:15:13.359 --> 00:15:14.799
I think there's a lot of reasons for

00:15:14.820 --> 00:15:15.019
that.

00:15:16.520 --> 00:15:18.642
And one of them is, well,

00:15:18.682 --> 00:15:20.722
he just happens to be God and he

00:15:21.964 --> 00:15:23.125
doesn't need to endure this.

00:15:23.144 --> 00:15:24.765
He's been abused by humankind

00:15:25.894 --> 00:15:26.754
since the beginning,

00:15:26.913 --> 00:15:31.416
and there's no reason for him to endure.

00:15:32.135 --> 00:15:32.716
Second of all,

00:15:32.755 --> 00:15:34.376
when the children of Yisrael,

00:15:34.397 --> 00:15:36.017
who were the control group that he was

00:15:36.057 --> 00:15:39.658
trying to use to demonstrate the benefits

00:15:39.698 --> 00:15:41.739
of listening to him and the consequence of

00:15:41.778 --> 00:15:43.899
rejecting him, told him,

00:15:44.179 --> 00:15:45.880
we never want to hear you speak to

00:15:45.961 --> 00:15:46.421
us again.

00:15:46.461 --> 00:15:48.022
We never want to see you again,

00:15:48.081 --> 00:15:50.182
not ever, under any circumstances.

00:15:50.221 --> 00:15:51.202
We'd rather die.

00:15:51.222 --> 00:15:55.364
That put God in a fairly tight position.

00:15:57.304 --> 00:15:59.605
where the only way to communicate now to

00:15:59.767 --> 00:16:03.807
the world would be through men and women.

00:16:03.888 --> 00:16:05.849
And overwhelmingly,

00:16:05.908 --> 00:16:08.350
God picks men through whom he

00:16:08.409 --> 00:16:09.071
communicates.

00:16:09.471 --> 00:16:10.370
He tells you who it is,

00:16:10.410 --> 00:16:11.192
and he works through them.

00:16:12.032 --> 00:16:14.533
So it is just consistent with what God

00:16:14.552 --> 00:16:15.433
has agreed to do,

00:16:15.494 --> 00:16:17.615
and God is always consistent.

00:16:19.436 --> 00:16:21.576
But I think there's another reason.

00:16:21.616 --> 00:16:24.817
Just as God is content to convey truth

00:16:25.164 --> 00:16:27.506
The option of knowing him and being part

00:16:27.626 --> 00:16:30.869
of his eternal family or rejecting him in

00:16:30.908 --> 00:16:32.971
such a way that he's easy to reject.

00:16:33.211 --> 00:16:34.272
And that is by design.

00:16:34.312 --> 00:16:36.894
God does not want a big family and

00:16:36.933 --> 00:16:37.453
forevermore.

00:16:37.514 --> 00:16:40.115
Heaven is not going to be crowded.

00:16:40.456 --> 00:16:42.618
If you are part of a popular religion,

00:16:43.118 --> 00:16:46.360
that religion is excluded just based on

00:16:46.400 --> 00:16:47.562
his popularity alone.

00:16:48.562 --> 00:16:51.804
So God is trying to make it exceedingly

00:16:51.985 --> 00:16:53.105
easy to reject him.

00:16:54.721 --> 00:16:56.721
Because he doesn't want to replicate the

00:16:56.761 --> 00:16:59.003
experience we've had here on earth these

00:16:59.043 --> 00:17:02.565
past six thousand years where man has just

00:17:02.705 --> 00:17:05.366
mucked everything up and been so

00:17:05.767 --> 00:17:08.008
enormously destructive with religion and

00:17:08.048 --> 00:17:08.588
politics.

00:17:10.950 --> 00:17:13.790
And so men are less convincing than God

00:17:13.811 --> 00:17:15.311
would be directly.

00:17:15.352 --> 00:17:18.973
So you get me at this time.

00:17:19.153 --> 00:17:19.355
Why?

00:17:19.414 --> 00:17:21.675
Because I'm less convincing than God would

00:17:21.715 --> 00:17:22.336
be directly.

00:17:22.355 --> 00:17:23.656
And that's by design.

00:17:25.794 --> 00:17:26.954
But I think there's another reason,

00:17:28.875 --> 00:17:29.936
and I think it may be the most

00:17:31.018 --> 00:17:31.698
important of all.

00:17:33.680 --> 00:17:36.342
When God chooses to convey his message

00:17:36.902 --> 00:17:37.942
through someone,

00:17:39.544 --> 00:17:42.906
that person becomes the exemplar that

00:17:43.067 --> 00:17:44.167
Israel forfeited.

00:17:44.488 --> 00:17:45.189
When Israel said,

00:17:45.229 --> 00:17:46.670
we don't want to hear from you again

00:17:46.730 --> 00:17:49.451
or see you again, when God found me,

00:17:49.491 --> 00:17:52.233
and I happened to be chosen not because

00:17:53.015 --> 00:17:53.075
of...

00:17:54.192 --> 00:17:55.772
Well, God may have had his reasons.

00:17:55.833 --> 00:17:57.233
I don't want to shortchange the reasons

00:17:57.273 --> 00:17:58.153
God made that choice.

00:17:58.213 --> 00:18:00.035
But the fact of the matter is there

00:18:00.055 --> 00:18:01.155
was no other choice.

00:18:03.356 --> 00:18:06.419
And when you recognize that,

00:18:07.419 --> 00:18:10.580
what God is essentially saying is I can

00:18:10.621 --> 00:18:13.102
choose to work with somebody who is

00:18:13.142 --> 00:18:15.304
otherwise a dunderhead, doesn't know me.

00:18:15.443 --> 00:18:16.703
I didn't know God's name at the time.

00:18:17.884 --> 00:18:20.866
Has no particular skill in any of these

00:18:20.906 --> 00:18:21.386
subjects.

00:18:22.874 --> 00:18:26.317
has no unusual, uncommon knowledge of God,

00:18:27.657 --> 00:18:31.500
but who is available to teach and to

00:18:31.560 --> 00:18:34.644
deploy because this individual has done

00:18:34.723 --> 00:18:38.166
what Abraham and Moshe had done,

00:18:38.547 --> 00:18:41.528
even Dowd had done,

00:18:41.548 --> 00:18:43.971
to walk away from religion and politics.

00:18:46.032 --> 00:18:48.795
You're never approachable by God until

00:18:48.835 --> 00:18:49.836
you've done those things.

00:18:50.056 --> 00:18:50.737
I had done them.

00:18:51.217 --> 00:18:52.157
Moshe had done them.

00:18:53.961 --> 00:18:54.761
Abraham had done them.

00:18:56.762 --> 00:19:00.164
And then you have the potential to become

00:19:00.204 --> 00:19:04.066
a clean slate that is open to God's

00:19:04.086 --> 00:19:04.507
teaching.

00:19:04.606 --> 00:19:06.508
And God's point of view here is that

00:19:06.988 --> 00:19:09.749
if I can take a clean slate that

00:19:09.788 --> 00:19:14.431
has the experience that he has rejected

00:19:14.851 --> 00:19:17.211
relative to religion and politics,

00:19:17.271 --> 00:19:19.292
which I did, which Moshe did,

00:19:19.353 --> 00:19:21.314
which Abraham did,

00:19:23.430 --> 00:19:26.832
Then if that individual does as I've

00:19:26.951 --> 00:19:30.253
asked, listens to me,

00:19:30.433 --> 00:19:32.894
and is open to my teaching and is

00:19:32.954 --> 00:19:34.016
guided by me,

00:19:34.635 --> 00:19:37.417
then I can teach that man everything he

00:19:37.458 --> 00:19:38.817
needs to know to be effective.

00:19:41.549 --> 00:19:42.111
In my case,

00:19:42.151 --> 00:19:44.653
it took twenty years before I really

00:19:44.692 --> 00:19:45.512
became effective.

00:19:45.573 --> 00:19:45.894
In fact,

00:19:46.034 --> 00:19:48.035
I would say twenty-two years from the

00:19:48.075 --> 00:19:49.355
beginning of our relationship.

00:19:49.717 --> 00:19:50.836
That's not entirely true.

00:19:50.856 --> 00:19:53.179
I think in the midst of that time,

00:19:53.219 --> 00:19:57.021
I was quite effective at excoriating the

00:19:57.082 --> 00:19:58.343
lies of Islam,

00:19:58.363 --> 00:20:00.064
proving that Allah was not God and that

00:20:00.104 --> 00:20:01.184
Muhammad was not a prophet.

00:20:01.244 --> 00:20:03.707
I was quite good at excoriating the lies

00:20:03.747 --> 00:20:04.708
of Christianity,

00:20:04.827 --> 00:20:06.709
proving that Jesus was not God,

00:20:06.808 --> 00:20:07.869
that he never existed,

00:20:07.910 --> 00:20:08.391
and that Paul

00:20:09.163 --> 00:20:10.325
was demon-possessed.

00:20:10.805 --> 00:20:12.306
The Christian New Testament has no

00:20:12.365 --> 00:20:12.885
validity.

00:20:13.747 --> 00:20:15.667
I was quite effective, I think,

00:20:16.009 --> 00:20:19.611
in determining over that time many

00:20:19.651 --> 00:20:21.731
thousands of profound insights that no one

00:20:21.751 --> 00:20:26.494
had previously conceived nor shared.

00:20:26.535 --> 00:20:29.136
But coming to the point where I could

00:20:29.156 --> 00:20:31.538
do this with you and just look into

00:20:31.618 --> 00:20:33.980
the camera and face you really directly

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:35.741
and speak directly to you in a live

00:20:35.801 --> 00:20:36.102
stream,

00:20:36.876 --> 00:20:39.199
It took twenty-two years of preparation,

00:20:39.239 --> 00:20:40.740
twenty-three years of preparation.

00:20:41.580 --> 00:20:43.542
But that's exactly as God wanted it to

00:20:43.583 --> 00:20:43.762
be.

00:20:44.804 --> 00:20:47.425
We had the time and we went through

00:20:47.445 --> 00:20:48.326
the process together.

00:20:49.207 --> 00:20:49.827
And God is saying,

00:20:50.228 --> 00:20:52.369
if this man could figure it out.

00:20:53.790 --> 00:20:57.653
Now it took twelve, fourteen hours a day,

00:20:58.015 --> 00:21:00.096
six and seven days a week for that

00:21:00.135 --> 00:21:00.997
twenty-two years,

00:21:01.257 --> 00:21:03.278
basically a hundred thousand hours.

00:21:04.605 --> 00:21:06.705
of thinking, of writing, of sharing,

00:21:06.766 --> 00:21:07.685
of translating,

00:21:09.586 --> 00:21:14.489
before I was properly taught to do this.

00:21:14.669 --> 00:21:20.771
And so what God is able to display

00:21:21.531 --> 00:21:23.492
is what would have happened had Israel

00:21:23.512 --> 00:21:25.614
done that.

00:21:25.673 --> 00:21:27.795
Had Israel listened to God as opposed to

00:21:28.335 --> 00:21:30.135
writing their own Talmud, Zohar.

00:21:31.734 --> 00:21:34.115
Had they responded to God as opposed to

00:21:34.155 --> 00:21:35.537
responded to men?

00:21:37.577 --> 00:21:39.239
Had they fallen in love with the Iowa's

00:21:39.298 --> 00:21:40.579
name rather than erased it?

00:21:41.160 --> 00:21:43.281
Had they come to embrace the great gift

00:21:43.301 --> 00:21:45.663
that was offered by Dowd,

00:21:45.702 --> 00:21:46.723
God's beloved son,

00:21:46.844 --> 00:21:49.704
our Messiah and King who serves as our

00:21:49.765 --> 00:21:50.246
savior,

00:21:51.946 --> 00:21:53.406
how different the world would have been.

00:21:53.426 --> 00:21:54.647
There would have been no Christianity,

00:21:54.708 --> 00:21:56.028
no Islam, no Judaism.

00:21:57.631 --> 00:22:01.212
And Jews would be the most prosperous and

00:22:01.252 --> 00:22:03.795
most beloved and enlightened and enabled

00:22:03.835 --> 00:22:04.474
people on earth.

00:22:07.537 --> 00:22:08.837
So God wanted to show it's possible.

00:22:09.878 --> 00:22:12.720
If he could take someone like me and

00:22:13.240 --> 00:22:15.102
teach him what he had to know to

00:22:15.162 --> 00:22:16.001
do this job,

00:22:16.041 --> 00:22:18.624
then it was possible for anyone to do

00:22:18.663 --> 00:22:20.105
this job, right?

00:22:21.411 --> 00:22:22.310
That was the purpose.

00:22:22.971 --> 00:22:24.991
That's why we did this together.

00:22:25.071 --> 00:22:27.471
And by going through all that process and

00:22:27.571 --> 00:22:29.952
every time that there was a challenge to

00:22:30.032 --> 00:22:33.973
have that obstacle obliterated and we step

00:22:34.134 --> 00:22:39.795
on top of a higher point with far

00:22:39.835 --> 00:22:44.036
greater knowledge and much greater

00:22:44.175 --> 00:22:44.976
understanding.

00:22:46.380 --> 00:22:48.040
such that we've reached a point now where

00:22:48.520 --> 00:22:51.801
new insights are being conveyed to us on

00:22:51.842 --> 00:22:52.843
a daily basis,

00:22:54.502 --> 00:22:56.163
then you come to trust God.

00:22:57.325 --> 00:22:58.565
Every time there's a challenge,

00:22:58.585 --> 00:23:00.905
he has an answer.

00:23:00.965 --> 00:23:01.846
Study his answer.

00:23:03.747 --> 00:23:04.728
Follow his example.

00:23:07.868 --> 00:23:09.410
You learn what's right,

00:23:09.430 --> 00:23:10.250
what's vindicating.

00:23:11.553 --> 00:23:15.035
especially with regard to those who are

00:23:15.134 --> 00:23:18.096
acting as if they were authorized,

00:23:18.135 --> 00:23:19.537
but yet are adversarial.

00:23:21.577 --> 00:23:25.180
And they are opposed to me.

00:23:25.980 --> 00:23:27.361
They were opposed to Yasha'yah.

00:23:28.240 --> 00:23:30.122
They're opposed to Yahowah.

00:23:30.182 --> 00:23:31.903
And Yahowah will try to console those

00:23:31.942 --> 00:23:32.502
individuals.

00:23:32.542 --> 00:23:35.765
He, you know, told, uh,

00:23:37.884 --> 00:23:38.403
Shamuw’el,

00:23:38.625 --> 00:23:41.086
when the children of Israel rebelled

00:23:41.145 --> 00:23:42.727
against him,

00:23:43.528 --> 00:23:45.128
