00:23:45.729 --> 00:23:46.148
Shamuw’el,

00:23:46.169 --> 00:23:47.730
they were rebelling against Jehovah.

00:23:49.571 --> 00:23:52.153
And sometimes he simply says, okay,

00:23:53.574 --> 00:23:54.095
I hear you.

00:23:54.355 --> 00:23:56.516
That's when Moshe had his meltdown and

00:23:56.556 --> 00:23:56.977
