But he did say,

00:24:07.221 --> 00:24:08.281
I got a couple of guys.

00:24:08.663 --> 00:24:09.823
You get them to the promised land,

00:24:09.863 --> 00:24:14.125
I'll take it from there.

00:24:14.205 --> 00:24:15.406
And so God has an answer.

00:24:17.567 --> 00:24:22.651
When Dowd couldn't fulfill the mission of

00:24:23.290 --> 00:24:27.173
