00:24:46.734 --> 00:24:47.355
the image,

00:24:47.996 --> 00:24:51.478
the prophecy that he was witnessing.

00:24:51.498 --> 00:24:51.698
You know,

00:24:51.738 --> 00:24:53.199
God simply sat him down and said,

00:24:53.219 --> 00:24:54.921
I'm going to explain it to you.

00:24:55.500 --> 00:24:57.001
And he did in no uncertain terms.

00:24:57.897 --> 00:25:01.219
Dowd realized that his associate was a man

00:25:01.259 --> 00:25:04.079
