00:25:04.119 --> 00:25:05.759
responsibility of getting that Ark of the

00:25:05.799 --> 00:25:09.201
Covenant properly positioned for Dowd to

00:25:09.260 --> 00:25:11.381
anoint the mercy seat upon his return on

00:25:11.421 --> 00:25:12.102
Yom Kippur.

00:25:12.301 --> 00:25:15.903
God had an answer.

00:25:15.942 --> 00:25:18.923
And so you learn to trust on God,

00:25:19.563 --> 00:25:23.544
trust God for the answer.

00:25:23.564 --> 00:25:25.345
The prophet Yasha'yah went on to say,

00:25:26.635 --> 00:25:29.897
You want to engage such that your way

00:25:29.958 --> 00:25:32.619
is straightforward and right before me and

00:25:32.660 --> 00:25:33.500
in my presence.

00:25:35.241 --> 00:25:38.202
God's not capricious.

00:25:38.363 --> 00:25:42.306
He is not circuitous.

00:25:42.326 --> 00:25:44.887
Religion is capricious and circuitous.

00:25:46.528 --> 00:25:47.709
It's full of contradictions.

00:25:48.150 --> 00:25:50.651
It requires God to be the God of

00:25:50.711 --> 00:25:51.451
contradictions.

00:25:52.618 --> 00:25:56.001
Christianity contradicts what God said and

00:25:56.061 --> 00:25:59.724
contradicts the Torah and contradicts the

00:25:59.765 --> 00:26:01.445
prophets and contradicts itself.

00:26:01.566 --> 00:26:04.888
Islam is just a stew of contradictions.

00:26:05.910 --> 00:26:08.832
So is Judaism.

00:26:08.852 --> 00:26:10.032
God's approach is straightforward.

00:26:11.354 --> 00:26:14.356
There is but one covenant, the Beryth.

00:26:15.136 --> 00:26:17.098
It has five conditions and five benefits.

00:26:18.039 --> 00:26:18.819
They've never changed.

00:26:18.839 --> 00:26:19.601
They will never change.

00:26:20.605 --> 00:26:23.008
God has seven steps that you can walk

00:26:23.048 --> 00:26:26.230
to him, one set of Mowed Miqrah,

00:26:26.910 --> 00:26:30.393
and they are eternal, unchanging.

00:26:31.133 --> 00:26:33.954
They don't fit into any religion, however.

00:26:33.974 --> 00:26:34.256
In fact,

00:26:34.336 --> 00:26:35.777
all religions are opposed to them,

00:26:35.817 --> 00:26:36.696
including Judaism.

00:26:38.699 --> 00:26:40.880
God has but one name, Chawah,

00:26:41.140 --> 00:26:44.403
and yet the religious are wont to ignore

00:26:44.442 --> 00:26:48.484
it or erase it or to change it.

00:26:48.505 --> 00:26:49.205
God's straightforward.

00:26:53.242 --> 00:26:54.282
He has but one son.

00:26:55.683 --> 00:26:56.304
We'll have many.

00:26:58.265 --> 00:26:58.884
One firstborn.

00:26:59.365 --> 00:26:59.785
It's Dowd.

00:27:00.905 --> 00:27:01.905
One anointed Messiah.

00:27:02.826 --> 00:27:05.606
Dowd.

00:27:05.727 --> 00:27:06.567
One returning king.

00:27:08.208 --> 00:27:08.468
Dowd.

00:27:10.949 --> 00:27:13.750
So it was then that in Yasha'yah forty

00:27:13.789 --> 00:27:18.551
that we read a call, a voice.

00:27:18.592 --> 00:27:19.152
Calls out.

00:27:20.471 --> 00:27:21.553
Inviting and summoning.

00:27:22.409 --> 00:27:28.834
reading and reciting in the mid bar which

00:27:28.933 --> 00:27:35.759
is the place where the word is questioned

00:27:35.778 --> 00:27:39.181
turn around and choose to change your

00:27:39.221 --> 00:27:43.884
direction such that you are prepared for

00:27:43.984 --> 00:27:46.547
the way of yangua

00:27:47.563 --> 00:27:48.723
of your own free will,

00:27:49.044 --> 00:27:50.944
choose to become straightforward and

00:27:51.005 --> 00:27:53.546
correct so that you are prepared for an

00:27:53.685 --> 00:27:56.788
elevated walkway through the dark and

00:27:56.928 --> 00:27:59.249
lifeless fabric of that which is

00:27:59.328 --> 00:28:04.711
commingled to approach our God.

00:28:06.813 --> 00:28:13.036
Yasha'yah, Isaiah, forty-two and three.

00:28:13.135 --> 00:28:13.635
A voice.

00:28:14.916 --> 00:28:15.217
God

00:28:16.163 --> 00:28:17.644
Speaks through men.

00:28:19.866 --> 00:28:20.346
And so.

00:28:20.968 --> 00:28:22.568
If you're going to listen to God.

00:28:22.608 --> 00:28:25.590
You're going to have to listen to the

00:28:25.631 --> 00:28:26.192
voice.

00:28:27.353 --> 00:28:29.453
Of the man that he has chosen to

00:28:29.513 --> 00:28:30.075
call out.

00:28:32.036 --> 00:28:32.936
And in this case.

